{"tid":693464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劇集播放量將破10億　馬浚偉搵定裸照找數","createTime":"2018-06-07T13:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T07:18:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a818fda2101cd08fc57940e4379c4664f16290fe","tid":693464,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"藝人胡定欣及馬浚偉到香港仔出席熱播劇《宮心計2深宮計》「齊心展愛心」活動，與一眾長者同樂。活動上更公布劇集於內地國粵語的播放量已達9.3億，正向10億邁進，首周「七天跨平台總收視」獲得27.8點，是2018年首周收視冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n有信心破10億<br />\n定欣與馬浚偉接受訪問，二人笑言有信心明天便突破10億，馬浚偉更說：「今、明兩晚劇情都幾慘痛，好虐心，內地朋友睇先兩集，都話劇情好慘。加上呢兩日天氣唔好，大家留喺屋企睇電視唔好出街喇！」馬浚偉又表示已分別準備好半裸照與全裸照，準備兌現10億承諾，問到想晒全裸還是半裸照？他笑說：「我想晒全裸多啲，不過張相好似未夠1歲，用鴨仔遮住咗重要部位！」定欣聞言亦表示考慮翻番舊照為20億做準備，提到或可拍張近照，馬浚偉笑言或會引起瘋傳！<br />\n<br />\n讚定欣歌舞出色<br />\n定欣及馬浚偉除了聯手宣傳劇集外，亦正為舞台劇密密做準備，馬浚偉指定欣歌舞表現好出色，自誇有眼光搵到好拍檔。他表示日前才聽過定欣唱崑曲，覺得對方有水準可以唱現場，定欣則笑言：「我都希望現場唱嘅，大家有期望就唔想令人失望，我對自己都有信心，不過我唱畀佢聽時都冇乜反應，可能佢要求低，我對自己要求就好高。」<br />\n<br />\n將去送別好友<br />\n提到馬浚偉的好友，有「香江才女」之稱的林燕妮辭世，並已定於6月26日舉行喪禮，正忙為舞台劇準備的他表示會到場送別好友：「我哋都係基督徒，對死亡有另一套睇法，大家終會喺天家相會，所以唔會太傷感。佢離開之前我哋有見過面，大家傾咗成個鐘，佢當時依然紅粉緋緋，我96年識佢，大家相識超過廿年，我一直叫佢『貴族』，佢就叫我浚偉。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607165007709-0607_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180607193032\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607165007709-0607_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180607193032&h=282bdf29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180607/bkn-20180607165007709-0607_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180607%2Fbkn-20180607165007709-0607_00862_001.html&d=K%2Fycj%2B51uPJsDx1t3aus4DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d07d7777\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180607/bkn-20180607165007709-0607_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8d0a1de7fd84a261c768bea23a00a266a7b19c24","tid":693464,"uid":129660,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"馬仔好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd0fc31db1847389047beccabb25522b403316d","tid":693464,"uid":21309,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T13:52:11.000Z","msg":"食屎啦條馬撚正一死狗公 想屌人咪出聲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a93abd96bbf4f941a0f7a2c642f1028e8cc26de","tid":693464,"uid":147264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T13:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ee7b56cd5d34bb9f33e910bf38428720082bb2","tid":693464,"uid":182930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"睇你條馬撚？"},{"pid":"4987b7f352d1b9e9860ad990be1210bdb96de1bd","tid":693464,"uid":132587,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.purinamills.com/2.purinamills.com/media/Images/MasterBrand/Lifestages/horse-special-needs.png?ext=.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.purinamills.com%2F2.purinamills.com%2Fmedia%2FImages%2FMasterBrand%2FLifestages%2Fhorse-special-needs.png%3Fext%3D.png&h=0e8d12ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬仔裸照"},{"pid":"a580b1ee9fd3fc049f45af4a2cf823fd5de99b6f","tid":693464,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0a1de7fd84a261c768bea23a00a266a7b19c24","tid":693464,"uid":129660,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"馬仔好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60b82990248cb4